Hellplague:

Hellplague was in the cockpit, slowly spinning the chair, tettering between consciousness and sleep cycle.  It had been quite some time since Malice and Blacknightmare had left, so it was just her and Celeron.  She looked up as she heard Celeron move about, wondering what he was up to.

